{"tid":1204203,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝警察叔叔","createTime":"2019-06-11T14:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T14:55:31.000Z","uid":224535,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"729b8e1ee6144ee215d1253460f44694e78c2bbb","tid":1204203,"uid":224535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:30:54.000Z","msg":"痴撚線睇live睇到火都黎，淨係識得聲大大咁恰啲同自己仔女咁上下年紀嘅學生，黑警知唔知醜。<br />\n<br />\n原本行完睇左結果無力感好大，睇完黑警咁樣搞我哋啲學生，仲搜埋學校真係嬲到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到而家搜學校搜老麥，容乜易上埋屋企。真係坐係屋企都唔安樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家即刻出黎，多謝警察叔叔比我搵返心入面個團火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb87f95e882be3ac62338727741e861b078c234","tid":1204203,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:46:01.000Z","msg":"議員 律師到場即刻收晒佢地皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004689f9b9a07e3b02019dadec0b11d9ae81b716","tid":1204203,"uid":68896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:48:00.000Z","msg":"雨傘都係由搞學生開始<br />\n<br />\n搞後生仔最犯眾憎"},{"pid":"b49e4e31b77394d5f97978f45762dbb2b06e26ac","tid":1204203,"uid":32455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abb87f95e882be3ac62338727741e861b078c234","tid":1204203,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:46:01.000Z","msg":"議員 律師到場即刻收晒佢地皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:55:31.000Z","msg":"啲議員第一次見到佢地咁型"}]}